            "role": "assistant",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "Contoso Electronics offers a lineup of consumer electronics and technology solutions, including smartphones, laptops, tablets, and smart home devices .\n\nFeatured Contoso products include :\n\n- **Contoso Smartphone X1** — **$799**; 6.5\" OLED display; 128GB/256GB storage; 48MP AI-enhanced main camera; 4500mAh battery with fast charging.\n- **Contoso Laptop Pro 15** — **$1,299**; 15.6\" 4K IPS display; Intel Core i7 (latest generation); 16GB RAM; 512GB NVMe SSD; up to 12 hours battery life.\n- **Contoso Smart Home Hub** — **$149**; Wi‑Fi 6, Bluetooth 5.0, Zigbee; built-in Contoso AI Assistant; compatible with 500+ smart home devices.\n\nSupport and warranty info :\n- **Support**: support@contoso.com; 1-800-CONTOSO; Mon–Fri 9AM–6PM EST  \n- **Warranty**: Standard 1-year manufacturer warranty; extended warranty available if purchased within 30 days of original purchase.\n\nIf you tell me which category you’re most interested in (phone, laptop, smart home), I can help compare options or recommend based on your needs.",
